        <li><strong>Ongoing Upgrades:</strong> Additional allocations for Selangor, Sabah, and Sarawak rural water supply</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>What This Means for Excavator Contractors:</strong></p>

      <p>Water treatment plants require extensive earthworks:
      </p>
